    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-model-kind session configuration. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each model kind dispatches against its own engine: language models use engine, STT models use sttEngine, TTS models use ttsEngine, and embedding models use embeddingEngine. All default to ::Tryll::InferenceEngine_Mock; set the ones you actually use. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
